# Secure Amazon S3 Bucket

## 📌 Overview

This project demonstrates how to securely configure an Amazon S3 bucket by implementing AWS security best practices.

The objective is to prevent unauthorized access, protect stored objects using encryption, enable versioning for recovery, and ensure that the bucket is monitored and ready for production use.

## 🎯 Business Scenario

A company wants to store employee documents in AWS.

